# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback. Any URL that isn't a built asset
# falls back to index.html so client-side routing (React Navigation)
# can handle the path. Without this, /open/:id deep links 404 on
# direct navigation.
#
# 200 status code (not 301/302) so the browser sees the SPA URL as
# authoritative — bookmarks + share-links to /open/:id behave correctly.

/*    /index.html    200
